Package fun.connor.fantasy.League

Class LeagueManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.fantasy.League.LeagueManager
  • public class LeagueManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The LeagueManager class provides a centralized way for other objects to interact with leagues. It contains all relevant methods to interact with individual leagues.
